snippet.title: Collective Unconscious [Launch Trailer]
snippet.description:
Available June 8th 2024, 3pm GMT.
https://ynoproject.net/

Collective Unconscious is a collaborative, multiplayer game that draws inspiration from Yume Nikki and its fangames. Discover new worlds, gather collectibles, and share a unique experience with your friends across the spirit world!

--

Trailer: Ayalunya
Animation: mitzyrie
Music: Noahrav, MaximumGuitar, orchidmantis
Collective Unconscious by the YNOproject community
